<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4359426>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Magnumtergalis aldarioarenasi n. sp. male. A. Habitus in lateral view. B. Frons and legs. C. Habitus in laterodorsal view, without legs and terminalia. D. Hind leg. E-G. Terminalia in lateral, dorsal and ventral views respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4359426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4359430>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Magnumtergalis albonigra n. comb. male holotype. A-B. Habitus in lateral and dorsal views respectively. C. Frons. D-G. Terminalia in lateral, dorsal, latero-ventral and ventral view respectively. Photos: M. Paris (MNCN)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4359430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

